miniToastr: function miniToastr ({title, message, type, timeout, cb, debugMsg}) {if (debugMsg) console[type](debugMsg) return miniToastr[type](message, title, timeout, cb)}
VueToasted: function VueToasted ({title, message, type, timeout, cb, debugMsg, position}) {if (debugMsg) console[type](debugMsg) if (type === VueNotifications.types.warn) type = 'show' return Vue.toasted[type](message, {duration: timeout}) }
VueEasyToast: function VueEasyToast ({title, message, type, timeout, cb, debugMsg, position}) {if (debugMsg) console[type](debugMsg)if (type === VueNotifications.types.warn) type = 'show' return Vue.toasted[type](message, {duration: timeout})}
toastr: function toastr ({title, message, type, timeout, cb, debugMsg, position}) { if (debugMsg) console[type](debugMsg) if (type === VueNotifications.types.warn) type = 'warning' return toastr[type](message, title, {timeOut: timeout})}
iziToast: function iziToast ({title, message, type, timeout, cb, debugMsg, position}) { if (debugMsg) console[type](debugMsg) if (type === VueNotifications.types.warn) type = 'warning' return iziToast[type]({title, message, timeout}) }
Noty: function Noty ({title, message, type, timeout, cb, debugMsg, position}) { if (debugMsg) console[type](debugMsg) if (type === VueNotifications.types.warn) type = 'warning' return new Noty({text: message, timeout, type}).show() }
swal: function swal ({title, message, type, timeout, cb, debugMsg, position}) { if (debugMsg) console[type](debugMsg) if (type === VueNotifications.types.warn) type = 'warning' return swal(title, message, type) }
